headline: $6.6 Million Grant From John Deere will Help Feed Americans Facing Hunger
summary: Deere & Company (NYSE:DE) today announced a $6.6 million, three-year commitment of unrestricted funding from the John Deere Foundation to Feeding America®. This grant reaffirms John Deere's commitment to hunger relief and supporting communities in need while honoring the work of farmers.

headline: Wall Street's Insights Into Key Metrics Ahead of Deere (DE) Q4 Earnings
summary: Beyond analysts' top -and-bottom-line estimates for Deere (DE), evaluate projections for some of its key metrics to gain a better insight into how the business might have performed for the quarter ended October 2024.
